  72:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     The compilation define USE_HAL_USART_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
  73:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
