 241:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     The HAL_USART_Init() function follows the USART synchronous SPI configuration
 242:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     procedure (details for the procedure are available in reference manual).
