 251:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 252:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |  M1 bit |  M0 bit |  PCE bit  |            USART frame                |
 253:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 254:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    8 bit data   | STB |     |
 255:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 256:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 7 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 257:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 258:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    0      |    | SB |    9 bit data   | STB |     |
 259:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
